column5: TECK So this headline explains it TECK is an odd bird a copper buffeted stock with really secondary to tertiary copper exposure right now and extremely solid fundamentals Of course as anyone who has been following Teck knows the copper part of the equation is set to become much larger in in 2436 months In the meantime though that doesnt mean its not overly influenced by headline articles such as this in SACopper rallies on Chinese plans to accelerate infrastructure financing
TECK This is all I got to say great news never seems to be enough for this stock but at least its real not BS
